8... Nxc3 9. bxc3 O-O { The position is completely equal by nature. } 10. Qh5
{ Only this move forces Black to weaken the kingside. } 10... f5
{ There is quite a lot of theory in this position, and I think there are just a few options left for White to fight for an advantage. Surgical accuracy is required from Black, though, as it is easy to get worse if Black is not careful. }
