{ Since  11.Bg5  is met by  11...Qe8  , White usually continues with the text move or  11.Re1  first, and it is hard to say which one is better. }
11... b6
{ In some lines, the inclusion of Rb1 and ...b6 is in White's favor, at other times it favors Black, but overall it shouldn't matter that much. }
12. Re1 c6 13. c4 Qf6 { This should be good enough for Black to equalize. } *

