11... dxc4 12. Bxc4 Nxc3 13. bxc3 b5 14. Bf1 Nc7 15. a4
{ This position is slightly but annoyingly better for White. There is no way for Black to clarify the position in any way, and therefore Black's strategy is to sit and wait. While Black has good chances to hold, there is no clear equality. }
