{ The latest fashion. In 2004 this was considered to be harmless, but modern engines have found new ways to pose problems to Black. }
9... Nxc3 10. bxc3 dxc4 11. Bxc4 Bf5
{ Now all Black needs to do is play ...Nd7, ... Qc7 and the game will be equal. }
