{ Now one of White's typical plans is to play  8.Be3  . } 8. Be3 Bxe3 9. fxe3
{ White's plan is to continue with Nh4-f5 or maybe Nd5, so Black usually plays  9...Ne7  10.d4  Ng6  with a complicated position - playable for White, probably okay for Black. }
