6... Qe7
{ As Black you will need to study some theory and memorize some lines here, but very powerful computers have already shown that Black always has enough counterplay for the pawn. }
7. Nxf7 { This doesn't work. } 7... d5
{ After this tactic Black is better - White either loses the f7-knight or loses two pieces for the rook on h8. }
