4. d4
{ This is an old line which is no longer so popular, but as White you could still try this, as Black does need to know what he is doing. }
4... exd4 5. e5 { This is the main point of 4. d4. } 5... Ne4
{ I think this move is also perfectly fine for Black, intending to follow up with ...d5. }
6. Qe2
{ At least this way White is preventing  6...d5  , as after  7.exd6  Black can't recapture on d6 with the knight. }
