{ If White castles then Black can - and should - take the pawn on e4. } 6...
Nxe4 7. cxd4 d5 { An important move to get in. } 8. dxc5 dxc4
{ Black is at least equal here, probably slightly better. 6. O-O is not dangerous at all. }
