20. Qxb7 Qd8 { And it is impossible for White to keep his extra pawn. } 21.
Red1 Qb8 22. Qxb8+ Rxb8 23. f3 Rxb4 24. Ne3
{ This is still not the end of the theory :@@EndBracket@@ There is a classic Giri-Aronian game where Aronian was saved by a miracle. I think that with a precise game Black can manage to make a draw. }
