{ At least the statistics of computer games seriously favor Black here. So we know that @@StartFEN@@r1bqkb1r/pppp1ppp/2n2n2/1B2p3/4P3/5N2/PPPP1PPP/RNBQK2R w KQkq - 4 4@@EndFEN@@  4.d4  is not that dangerous. }
