{ Now actually this position is quite playable for Black. Of course the most important test of this 5...a6 move is d4. }
7. d4 { So d4 is an important move but maybe Black can equalize here. } 7...
exd4 8. Nxd4
{ Or  8.Qxd4  Be7  9.Nc3  .  But it's better to try to take with the knight if you really want to fight for an advantage because the c6-pawn is hanging. }
