{ And it seems that computers are managing to equalize here with Black after some very strange play. }
9. Nc6 Qd7 10. Na5
{ Perhaps if White had managed to move a knight to c3, this would have probably been better. }
10... Qa4 11. Qe1 Be7
{ I don't know what modern computers and powerful computers are saying about this position now but at that time, I thought it was quite close to equality. }
