{ This has been played a lot by players like Aronian and Hikaru Nakamura but it's out of fashion nowadays. It might be fine - it's not a bad move at all, but White has more chances to get some advantage and I think that there are different tries which you can check it yourself later. But my choice would be between  6...d6  and  6...d5  . }
