7... Qf6
{ There is a lot of theory here but Black is definitely doing fine. All in all, it's a playable variation, and for White, it's easy to learn. But frankly, objectively speaking, it's not very dangerous for Black. Black can choose one of the systems I presented and will not experience any problems. }
