7. Re1 d5 8. Nxd4 Bd6 9. Nxc6 Bxh2+ { The idea behind Black's play. } 10. Kh1
{ Leading by force to a better endgame.   10.Kxh2  Qh4+  would lead to a perpetual. }
10... Qh4 11. Rxe4+ dxe4 12. Qd8+ Qxd8 13. Nxd8+ Kxd8 14. Kxh2
{ Capablanca beat Lasker here and since then players have tried to prove that Black has equal chances but to no avail. }
