{ A nice counterattacking blow, simultaneously attacking both d5 and a8. } 18.
Rxc1 Rxa8 19. Rd3
{ White is an exchange up, but the knight on a3 is pretty bad and Black's bishops are quite powerful on their diagonals - it seems that Black is holding - and computer agrees. }
