8... O-O
{ The standard move. This position can also arise after @@StartFEN@@r1bqk2r/2ppbppp/p1n2n2/1p2p3/4P3/1B1P1N2/PPP2PPP/RNBQ1RK1 b kq - 1 7@@EndFEN@@  7...O-O  8.a3  d6  . }
