Ne3 Nc7 { Simply trying to go Bg5. } 17. Nf5 Ne6
{ Computers consider this position to be fine - there is once again counterplay along the b-file that compensate for the absence of the bishop pair @@StartBracket@@and the strong knight on f5@@EndBracket@@. }
