13... Bh5
{ The retreat of the bishop is met strongly with the advance of the g-pawn. }
14. g4 Bg6 15. Nbd2 { And now White's knight is free to recapture on d4. }
15... cxd4 16. Nxd4 { And White has an advantage. } *

