21. Bd2
{ And I remember that this position was considered to be playable for Black, as one of the possible plans involved maneuvering the dark-squared bishop to b6. But nowadays, the statistics are overwhelmingly in White's favor, @@StartBracket@@especially in computer games. @@EndBracket@@ which probably means White is objectively better.With the knight on a5, it is not so hard to believe and I definitely don't recommend you to play this line. }
